"<guimenu>सम्पादयतु</guimenu> <guimenuitem>कब्जितस्थानस्य गणनां कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calculates occupied space</link> of files and "
