msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>गच्छ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>लोकप्रिय &URL;s...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a listing of frequently viewed folders from which you may navigate "
"to one by double-clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"बहुधा दृश्यमानानां पुटस्य सूचीं प्रदर्शयति यस्मात् भवन्तः तस्मिन् द्विवारं क्लिक् कृत्वा एकस्मिन् "
"गन्तुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
